window.bookSummaryJSON = "<b>The astonishing sequel to <i>Children of Time</i>, the award-winning novel of humanity's battle for survival on a terraformed planet.</b><br><br>Thousands of years ago, Earth's terraforming program took to the stars. On the world they called Nod, scientists discovered alien life -- but it was their mission to overwrite it with the memory of Earth. Then humanity's great empire fell, and the program's decisions were lost to time.<br><br>Aeons later, humanity and its new spider allies detected fragmentary radio signals between the stars. They dispatched an exploration vessel, hoping to find cousins from old Earth.<br><br>But those ancient terraformers woke something on Nod better left undisturbed."; 
